survey_response.review_text: I, Smita Shivalkar, went through surgery performed by Dr. Vipin Mahurkar, Periodontist, assisted by Dr Dhwani Kapadia.  They performed the surgery of implants in place of missing teeth. The procedure was totally painless thanks to good anaesthesia. One thing i had noticed that Dr Dhwani has a very light hand which gave me the satisfaction of being in safe hands. With a  few follow-up appointments Dr Dhwani was working patiently on me to help me replace the lost teeth as well as my smile and make me comfortable whenever i needed to.  Thank you to her patiance & ability to handal the patients well. I would recommend.
